title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - Colin’s Rams/Niners MNF Instant Reaction
itunes:title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - Colin’s Rams/Niners MNF Instant Reaction
description:
Colin gives his instant reaction to the Niners convincing 24-9 Monday Night Football win over the Rams, including if he thinks the Niners are a Super Bowl contender with Jimmy G, and why the Rams’ offense is having a Super Bowl hangover.
